The Australian Integrated Forecast System (AIFS) bụ UNIX na Linux -based nhazi, ngosi, nyocha na nkwukọrịta usoro màkà data ihu igwe.
Ọ na-agụnye ụlọ ọrụ màkà iri na nchekwa nke ihe ndị na-ahụ màkà ihu igwe na mmiri, nkè enwere ike igosi, nyochaa ma jiri ya mee ihe na ihuenyo
A na-enyekwa ngwá ọrụ màkà ịdọ áká ná ntị, atụmatụ eserese na nkwadebe na mgbasa nke amụma na ịdọ aka na ntị nye ọha na eze.
AIFS na arụ ọrụ na nyiwe AIX, HP-UX na Linux na Australia, Fiji, Indonesia na Malaysia.
Mmepe malitere n'afọ 1991 dị ka ónyé nọchiri ányá Automated Regional Operations System (AROS), nke e wuru na ụlọ Tandem NonStop.
